name: Annakila Jepsen
bio: Annakila is currently in her sophomore year studying Computer Science and Mathematics, and she will be launching a start up company in digital marketing within the next year. She hopes to later pursue a career in AI and VR. She is a passionate Sci-Fi junkie, and devoted fur mom. In her free time she can be found playing pool, painting, or traveling the world in search of the best sky-diving locations.
